[size=4][b]Description[/b][/size]
[size=3][color=#D4D4D8]A reworked Simplified Chinese localization for [i]Into the Radius 2[/i].

Built from the current game EnglishSource data.

[b]Compatibility:[/b] Built from the local game resources containing Update 1.1.2 main-menu notes. If the Steam build changes, please check for an updated release.

Features:
• 3,300+ source keys / 6,600+ locres rows across both namespaces
• Reworked terminology and long-form narrative text
• Maple Mono NF CN font files included for CJK rendering
• Font license: Maple Mono NF CN is licensed under SIL Open Font License 1.1; the license text is included in the archive
• Free, complete, and manually verified & polished
• A cleaner alternative to incomplete paid machine-translation packs

[b]Known Issues:[/b]
• The game currently swaps the IZh-27 6x Cartridge Belt (L)/(R) labels. This pack compensates by flipping the Chinese text accordingly. If a future game update fixes this, the belt names may appear reversed — an updated translation will be released.
• There are still 2 places in the main flow where we cannot override the translated text for now. This doesn't affect gameplay:
[img]https://github.com/jojuniori/ITR2_CN_Localization/raw/main/screenshot/untransed.png[/img][/color][/size]

[size=4][b]Installation[/b][/size]
[size=3][color=#D4D4D8][b]Vortex[/b]

Install the zip with Vortex and enable it.

[b]Manual[/b]

Extract the archive and copy:
[code]z_IntoTheRadius2_SimplifiedChinese_Localization_P.pak[/code]

to:
[code]SteamLibrary\steamapps\common\IntoTheRadius2\IntoTheRadius2\Content\Paks\[/code]

[b]Uninstall[/b]

Delete the pak file above.[/color][/size]

